        registry.enableSimpleBroker("/topic", "/queue");

        // Client sends messages to /app/... (if client needs to send to server)
        registry.setApplicationDestinationPrefixes("/app");

        // /user/queue/orders → only sent to specific user, not broadcast
        registry.setUserDestinationPrefix("/user");
    }

    @Override
    public void registerStompEndpoints(StompEndpointRegistry registry) {
        registry.addEndpoint("/ws")
            .setAllowedOriginPatterns("*")
            .withSockJS();  // SockJS fallback for browsers without WebSocket support
    }
}
```

**STOMP concepts:**
```text
/topic/global-updates  → broadcast to ALL subscribers (e.g., public price updates)
/user/{userId}/queue/orders → delivered only to user with that userId
```

