## What the user sees

```text
User places order:
  Browser opens WebSocket to /ws
  Subscribes to /user/queue/order-updates

Order goes PLACED → PROCESSING (30 seconds later):
  Kafka event fires → WebSocket pusher sends to userId
  Browser receives: {"orderId":"abc","status":"PROCESSING"}
  Page updates WITHOUT user doing anything

Order goes PROCESSING → SHIPPED (1 hour later):
  Same flow
  Browser receives: {"orderId":"abc","status":"SHIPPED","trackingNumber":"JD123"}
